data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Welcome home to this beautiful Atwater/Oasis model in the highly sought after community of Harrison Ranch. This 3 bed/ 2 bath + bonus room home sits on a pond, where you can watch the beautiful sunrise while sipping on your coffee. The upgrades start outside with well-manicured landscaping. This home offers an open floorplan and provides plenty of space for entertaining. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, granite counters, cabinets with crown molding, and an island that provides extra storage. The backyard has a screened lanai where you can enjoy the beautiful Florida weather and wildlife. There is also plenty of space to add on your own pool. The master bedroom has a large walk-in closet and a master bathroom with dual sinks, water closet, and a walk-in shower. The split floor plan puts the other two bedrooms and bathroom at the other end of the house. There is also a bonus room at the front of the house, which is perfect for a home office/den or could be converted into a 4th bedroom. The home is equipped with hurricane shutters, and an irrigation system with reclaimed water. Recent school rezoning has Harrison Ranch going to a brand new Elementary & High School, which opened in 2019 as well as a highly rated middle school. Harrison Ranch offers a 24 hour gym, heated junior Olympic pool, tennis/pickleball/basketball courts, playgrounds, ball fields, and 5.5 miles of beautiful hiking trails. An activity director is also on-site, putting on fun events for young families as well as active adults. Tampa, St. Pete, Sarasota and beautiful beaches are all within 45 minutes, making this a perfect central location. Harrison Ranch offers you a beautiful community and a lifestyle you can truly enjoy.
